source_unavailable.description:
WattPlan could not read any fresh data from the configured {source_name}, and {grace_note}

**After that, {consequence}**

What you can do:
- {action}
- Open the WattPlan setup and check the selected source
- Wait for the next refresh if the source is only temporarily unavailable

source_incomplete.description:
The configured {source_name} only covers about {covered_hours} hours, but WattPlan needs {required_hours} hours for this setup. This may mean the selected provider is not returning enough forecast data to cover the full planning period.

{grace_note}

**After that, {consequence}**

What you can do:
- {action}
- Open the WattPlan setup and inspect the selected source
